\f0\b\fs34 \cf2 How Time Moves: Methodology Summary
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
The Democracy Clock moves in discrete increments based on documented events. There are no preset weekly or monthly movement targets, and no effort is made to smooth or balance outcomes for narrative effect. When events warrant significant movement, the clock reflects that magnitude.\
\
Events are evaluated independently, then aggregated to determine net movement over a defined reporting period. No single event automatically determines trajectory; however, sustained patterns of institutional behavior carry cumulative weight.\
\
All clock movements are traceable to logged events. The methodology is applied consistently across time periods. When historical recalibration is necessary\'97for example, due to newly available information or clarified precedent\'97it is documented transparently rather than silently revised.\
\
The objective is not precision to the minute, but 
\f2\b consistency of judgment over time
\f1\b0 .\
